          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The separation-time activities of Nb-95-m and",
                "Nb-95-g were determined from a least-square fit of the",
                "observed Nb-95-g activity as function of cooling time,",
                "using standard decay-growth equations. In order to",
                "calculate the independent isomeric yield ratio also",
                "knowledge of the contribution of the decay of the",
                "precursor Zr-95 to the Nb-95-g activity was required.",
                "This was determined, in a similar way, from a separate",
                "measurement ( 72-76%)."
              ]
            }
          ],
